Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:51.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:19.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NYou don't have to be, like, sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:25.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, you'll get to join\Nher after I exclude you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:27.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:34.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] From the beginning,\Nwe hated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,But also, we loved you\Nfrom the beginning, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,All we wanted was to become\Ntrue friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:46.06,Main,,0,0,0,,So we had to cross the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGinko, Kure-pie, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu loves you. She loves\Nboth of you, so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:12.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:15.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NAttention, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:48.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Above all things, we must\Nremain way invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:52.00,Main,,0,0,0,,The time has come to begin\Nthe Exclusion Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:54.38,Main,,0,0,0,,"Friends" are, like, more\Nimportant than anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:57.97,Main,,0,0,0,,agreed? The friends gathered\Nhere right now are Us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:59.39,Main,,0,0,0,,We are Us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Those who, like, dare to\Ncontradict Our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:04.10,Main,,0,0,0,,are a disgrace, like, totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,As are those who want to, like,\Nway stick out from our crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.81,Main,,0,0,0,,The ones that, like,\Nrefuse to fit in with Us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:14.11,Main,,0,0,0,,are nothing but a nuisance.\NPeople like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,those who, like, don't follow\Nsocial cues, are way evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Humans and bears have\Nbeen, like, way severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:25.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yet still, certain people are,\Nlike, trying to cross that wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:28.33,Main,,0,0,0,,We're here to decide who that\Nnext evil will be so we can,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,like, way exclude them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:34.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's, like, search evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:03.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO chuckles]\NSelect! We have our evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:07.08,Main,,0,0,0,,So, is everyone,\Nlike, totally ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,All right. We will now, like,\Ntotally exclude the evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:18.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Nega-kuma energy,\Nreplenishing and ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:23.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NBuzz, buzz! Nasty, nasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNasty, nasty, nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Nasty, nasty, nasty,\Nnasty, nasty, nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Shoot her with that, and\Nshe gets way blown to bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.86,Main,,0,0,0,,The bear will be extinct\Nin, like, no time flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:39.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on! I'm the evil,\Nisn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,All you really have\Nto do is exclude me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO chuckles]\NOf course,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,that's exactly\Nwhat we plan to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:50.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\N♪ Yuri ga aku. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:52.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NThis will be your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.13,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get to kill your\Nfriend, so we don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] You don't follow\Nthis world's rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.88,Main,,0,0,0,,so you're, like, way evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,We all stay invisible
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,because we don't wanna\Nbe anything like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:13.69,Main,,0,0,0,,But, if you're invisible, how\Nare you ever going to be found?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:14.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:17.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NMy friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to be kidding.\NGrowl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:25.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous, that girl\Nis hardly a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:27.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I came here to eat\NKureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,From the beginning,\Nthat's all I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha is my prey,\Nnothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:35.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never once thought\Nof that girl as my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not my friend.\NKureha Tsubaki's not my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:46.97,Main,,0,0,0,,--[CHOUKO grunts] Lia--\N--[KUREHA] That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you're lying, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.06,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're telling the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.86,Main,,0,0,0,,then why did you cross\Nthe wall and come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] Because I wanted\Nto eat you. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:06.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] And if that's true,\Nwhy did you stay by my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Why save me?\NYou both did what you could
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.54,Main,,0,0,0,,to protect me from\Nthe Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That's because if you\Nhad become invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.92,Main,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't have\Ntasted as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:21.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You can stop this now, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:24.88,Main,,0,0,0,,From the very beginning,\Nyou were my true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:28.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You crossed the wall,\Nand you found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,You saved me from the Invisible\NStorm, and gave me love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:38.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Look, I am only your enemy.\NAll I wanted was to eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:44.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Get it now? I'm a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.82,Main,,0,0,0,,The bear has revealed\Nher true form to Us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, exclude that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS] Exclude! Exclude!\NExclude! Exclude! Exclude...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:04.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Oh, yes,\NI remember everything, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NPlease stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL A] We have to\Nexclude all traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS] Exclude! Exclude!\NExclude! Exclude! Exclude...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:33.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Does she not get to be\Napproved 'cause she's a bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:37.58,Main,,0,0,0,,--But why? Is being a bear bad?\N--[GINKO sighs] Growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:40.79,Main,,0,0,0,,If... If she were a human girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:43.96,Main,,0,0,0,,would we be able to\Nbe together forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:46.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Would I be able\Nto protect Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Lady Kumaria. Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm the one who\Nhoped for a Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,This is my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:58.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NKureha Tsubaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.08,Main,,0,0,0,,this is a challenge from\Nthe Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:18.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYes, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] If they grant a bear\Nyuri approval in court,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.96,Main,,0,0,0,,she can become a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:29.43,Main,,0,0,0,,But to do that, you have\Nto let go of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:31.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's usually whatever\Nyou care about the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Well, and this\Nis just Lulu's theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,but Lulu bets in Ginko's trial,\Nwhen they made her let go
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:43.02,Main,,0,0,0,,of something, she had to\Nlet go of your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:46.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NSorry, Lulu, you were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:50.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko didn't choose to let go of\Nher love in order to get a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,--It wasn't her.\N--[door opens]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NIt was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:04.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NLet the Yuri Trial begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant human Kureha Tsubaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:09.09,Main,,0,0,0,,is there anything you\Nwould like to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be with\NGinko forever, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.43,Main,,0,0,0,,So, I was hoping, that, maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.97,Main,,0,0,0,,you could make Ginko\Na human girl like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Honor, the defendant\Nhas obviously just committed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:23.06,Main,,0,0,0,,the crime of pride. Therefore,\Nthe court must find her guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Crime of pride?\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Basically, it's about\Nyou wanting to transform
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro from\Na bear into a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,But I have to change\Nher. Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Because bears all get excluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:37.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NHm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] And I know Ginko\Nwill be much happier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,as a human anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE BEAUTY] Whoa, someone's\Nconfident! Sparkle, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:49.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL] And that is exactly\Nwhat we're telling you is pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:52.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't care if\Nit's pride, or a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, I want you to\Nmake Ginko a human girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:10:00.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Very well.\NHowever, there is one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:04.56,Main,,0,0,0,,In order for your wish to come\Ntrue, you must relinquish love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Without love,\Nyou'll forget all about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.44,Main,,0,0,0,,your precious\Nfriend, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:10.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NWhen you wake up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,understand that you will\Nmost likely reject her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Reject Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:24.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] That day, I made a wish\Nthat no one should ever make.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I was foolish enough to\Nbelieve my selfish love
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,was actually the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:34.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] You must wait.\NOne day the time will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,When the Invisible\NStorm arrives,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,you will find Ginko\NYurishiro again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL] If you can make\Nfriends with her once more,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,you must then exchange\NPromise Kisses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:49.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE BEAUTY] After that,\Nyou can be together forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:52.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:55.82,Main,,0,0,0,,And now, defendant human\NKureha Tsubaki, I ask you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.99,Main,,0,0,0,,will you choose to make Ginko\NYurishiro a human girl like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Or will you choose\Nto give up on love?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:04.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Sir, I refuse to ever\Ngive up on love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:07.58,Main,,0,0,0,,So, please, make Ginko\Na human girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NLulu, I hate to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:14.55,Main,,0,0,0,,but I'm afraid I wished\Nfor Ginko to be human,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:17.97,Main,,0,0,0,,and I did it in exchange\Nfor what was most precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:25.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NLet the Yuri Trial begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:39.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NDefendant human Kureha Tsubaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:42.08,Main,,0,0,0,,are you ready to\Nadmit your crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:46.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I admit that I have previously\Ncommitted the crime of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I did so by asking you to turn\NGinko into a human girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE BEAUTY, LIFE COOL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:54.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Now let me ask, when you\Nsearched the Invisible Storm,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:58.13,Main,,0,0,0,,did you find what you wanted\Nto find? What you hoped to find?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I met a girl there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NShe taught me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.36,Main,,0,0,0,,She found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:23.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I found what I wanted.\NI found true love with Sumika!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NSumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI'm not afraid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:44.93,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as I don't forget love,\NI'll never, ever be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:48.27,Main,,0,0,0,,If I don't give up on love,\Neven if I lose something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:51.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never be invisible. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm free, now, and I will\Nleap into the storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:01.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:07.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Lulu, thank you. I'll\Ntake this star, this true love,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.91,Main,,0,0,0,,and deliver it to Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Face it, Ginko,\Nyou are my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,No! You're wrong! You're no\Nfriend of mine! Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a people-eating bear,\NGinko the Lone Wolfsbane,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.45,Main,,0,0,0,,and I came here to eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:50.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop. Stay back!\NHurry up and shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:54.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I'll eat all of you!\NI'm a criminal bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:04.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, Kureha, stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.\NI finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:24.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Help me with my wish!\NLady Kumaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's Lady Kumaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, how wonderful,\Nshe's regaining her form!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed, she hath returneth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.42,Main,,0,0,0,,which means we gots to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,For this is sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL]\NThis is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE BEAUTY]\NSparkle, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:33.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki, is your\Nlove the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I will smash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:53.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I will smash my image!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:59.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Lady Kumaria,\Nmake my wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I... wanna be... a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:20.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS sigh]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Ew!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:49.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:55.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, how could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:02.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Ginko, thank you\Nfor refusing to forget love,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:05.44,Main,,0,0,0,,and thank you for never,\Never giving up on it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It's for you,\Nmy Promise Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NDid you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:38.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You and me are gonna\Nbe together forever now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:41.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NTogether forever. Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:18:02.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, KUREHA]\NYuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NThat's, like, way unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,A human, like, became... a bear?\NUh! Like... way... gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:31.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[UKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't do it.\NStop! No shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:50.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, hey. What are you,\Nlike, waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:55.26,Main,,0,0,0,,That thing's not human anymore!\NIt's a bear! It's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:00.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, exclude them!\NWe have to exclude all evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Aim straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:09.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.99,Main,,0,0,0,,--Don't think about it!\N--[STUDENTS whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:53.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NWe worked hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,we worked together,\Nand we got the job done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Ladies, we successfully\Nexcluded the terrible evil
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:05.79,Main,,0,0,0,,that had been overrunning\Nthis school for far too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[applause]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:10.71,Main,,0,0,0,,What's more,\Nwe know we've been right,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:13.13,Main,,0,0,0,,and should remain\Ninvisible at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's begin the\NExclusion Ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\N"Friends" are more important
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,than anything else, agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:25.52,Main,,0,0,0,,The friends gathered here,\Nright now, are Us. We are Us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:28.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[UKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:11.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] The ones who\Nrefuse to fit in with Us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:14.36,Main,,0,0,0,,are nothing but a nuisance.\NPeople like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:17.53,Main,,0,0,0,,those who don't follow\Nsocial cues, are evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:23.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let us decide on\Nthe next evil to exclude!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:29.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT crying]\NNasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[crying continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:42.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[KONOMI-BOT]\NNasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,--Nasty? Nasty?\N--[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:21:58.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:27.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] "And so, having\Ncompleted their Promise Kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:30.02,Main,,0,0,0,,the two began a journey\Nbeyond severance,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:32.89,Main,,0,0,0,,guided by the star of love."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:35.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Big Sis, Lulu, I wish\Nthis wasn't the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:38.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you know what happened\Nto them after they left?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a very good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:43.53,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think\Nhappened, Milne?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:46.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[MILNE]\NHmmm. I dunno!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:50.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think I figured\Nout something else, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:53.71,Main,,0,0,0,,--[MILNE] Smooch!\N--[LULU] Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I should've just done it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.46,0:22:58.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I could've given you\Nthe Promise Kiss instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.17,0:22:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Milne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.55,0:23:00.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:05.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] We'll be\Ntogether forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:09.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[MILNE] Mm-hm! Big Sis,\NLulu. I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:16.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NI love you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.93,0:23:52.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[LADY KUMARIA] And so, no one\Nknows where the girls have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.81,0:23:56.31,Main,,0,0,0,,But, that is as it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.39,0:23:57.90,Main,,0,0,0,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,it is with your own love that\Nthe world awakens and changes.
